Package: celltypeNN
Type: Package
Title: Deep Learning Framework for Cell Type Prediction from Single-Cell Multi-Modal Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Your", "Name", email = "your.email@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: An R implementation of CellType-NN, a deep learning framework for
    cell type prediction from single-cell multi-modal data including scRNA-seq,
    CITE-seq, and ATAC-seq. Provides neural network architectures, preprocessing
    pipelines, and evaluation metrics for automated cell type classification.
